# here locally without committing them.
docs/

# Comprehension-gate explanation artifacts. These document AI-generated
# changes per-commit and may contain identifying details about the
# maintainer's reasoning. Kept out of the public repo by default; live in
# your private workspace if needed.
dot_claude/explanations/
